{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/docker/docker-structure-windows10/","webpackCompilationHash":"9bc18b594d2407556304","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"renuevo blog","author":"deokhwa kim","siteUrl":"https://renuevo.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"https-renuevo-github-io","utterances":""},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ec0912f1-5f1b-543c-9049-c1a3a525dcb6","excerpt":"Docker의 기본 구조 이번 포스트에서는 와 가 있어야만 Docker 설치가 가능한 이유를 알아 보도록 하겠습니다   서버 가상화 (Virtual Machine) 먼저 서버 가상화 기술 2가지에 대해 알아 보겠습니다      하이퍼바이저 Type1 가상화 하이퍼바이저 Type1은 Windows에서 지원하는 가 있습니다 하드웨어를 이용한 가상화 기술로 효율적인 가상화가 가능합니다   하이퍼바이저 Type2(호스트형) 가상화 호스트형 서버 가상화에는 가 있습니다 Host OS…","html":"<h1 id=\"docker의-기본-구조\"><a href=\"#docker%EC%9D%98-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"docker의 기본 구조 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Docker의 기본 구조</h1>\n<p>이번 포스트에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">가상화 기술의 3가지</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">Windows10에서 Hyper-V</code>가 있어야만 Docker 설치가 가능한 이유를 알아 보도록 하겠습니다  </p>\n<h2 id=\"서버-가상화-virtual-machine\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94-virtual-machine\" aria-label=\"서버 가상화 virtual machine permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>서버 가상화 (Virtual Machine)</h2>\n<p>먼저 서버 가상화 기술 2가지에 대해 알아 보겠습니다  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 690px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.34394904458599%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Server Virtual\"\n        title=\"Server Virtual\"\n        src=\"/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/36727/hypervisor.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/acf4b/hypervisor.png 173w,\n/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/fc834/hypervisor.png 345w,\n/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/36727/hypervisor.png 690w,\n/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/17fa4/hypervisor.png 1035w,\n/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/a5044/hypervisor.png 1380w,\n/static/0603b7f09d3bd0236f0995594e6a2aba/a0d55/hypervisor.png 1570w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>  </p>\n<br/>\n<ol>\n<li>하이퍼바이저 Type1 가상화<br>\n하이퍼바이저 Type1은 Windows에서 지원하는 <code class=\"language-text\">Hyper-V</code>가 있습니다<br>\n하드웨어를 이용한 가상화 기술로 효율적인 가상화가 가능합니다  </li>\n</ol>\n<br/>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>하이퍼바이저 Type2(호스트형) 가상화<br>\n호스트형 서버 가상화에는 <code class=\"language-text\">VMware Server</code>가 있습니다<br>\nHost OS위에 가상환경을 만들어 Guest OS를 설치하는 가상화 기술입니다<br>\n하드웨어 및 가상환경이 호스트 OS에 의지하고 있기 때문에 속도가 느립니다   </li>\n</ol>\n<br/>\n<h3 id=\"전가상화와-반가상화\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%84%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EB%B0%98%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"전가상화와 반가상화 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>전가상화와 반가상화</h3>\n<p>일반적으로 이 두가지 Type과 같이 나오는 개념이 <code class=\"language-text\">전가상화</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">반가상화</code>라는 개념이 있습니다<br>\n<strong>반가상화가 전가상화에 비해 상대적으로 성능이 좋습니다</strong><br>\nType1을 전가상화 Type2를 반가상화라고 설명하는 글들을 볼 수 있는데 이는 전부 옛말입니다<br>\n요즘은 <code class=\"language-text\">전/반가상화</code>를 혼재해서 사용하는 경우가 많습니다  </p>\n<p>보다 자세한 개념은 <a href=\"https://itholic.github.io/hypervisor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">하이퍼바이저, 전가상화, 반가상화</a> 포스팅을 참고하시기 바랍니다    </p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"컨테이너화-containers\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88%ED%99%94-containers\" aria-label=\"컨테이너화 containers permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>컨테이너화 (Containers)</h2>\n<p><strong>컨테이너화는 Docker에서 사용하는 가상화 기술입니다</strong><br>\nVM과 헷갈리기 쉬워 <a href=\"https://www.docker.com/blog/containers-are-not-vms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Containers are not VMs</a>라는 글이 정식으로 등록되기도 했습니다<br>\n그림으로 서로 어떻게 다른지 살펴보겠습니다  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 690px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"containers-vm\"\n        title=\"containers-vm\"\n        src=\"/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/36727/docker-structure.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/acf4b/docker-structure.png 173w,\n/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/fc834/docker-structure.png 345w,\n/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/36727/docker-structure.png 690w,\n/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/17fa4/docker-structure.png 1035w,\n/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/a5044/docker-structure.png 1380w,\n/static/329b5717228e6947915aeb166bdf91bf/2f950/docker-structure.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br>\n<span class='img_caption'>Source : <a href=\"https://www.docker.com/blog/containers-and-vms-together/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Docker Blog</a></span>  </p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Containers</code>는 Host OS위에서 동작합니다<br>\nDocker는 추상화를 통해 Host OS 커널을 공유 하면서 각 App Container들이 필요로 하는 요소만을 패킹징하여 제공합니다<br>\n이러한 요소때문에 각각의 OS를 가져야하는 일반적인 가상화 보다 효율적이게 작동할 수 있습니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>하지만 Host OS 커널에 의존하기 때문에 OS가 다른 경우 오른쪽 그림처럼 VM과 Docker를 같이 사용하는 경우도 존재 합니다</strong>  </p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"windows10-hyper-v와-docker\"><a href=\"#windows10-hyper-v%EC%99%80-docker\" aria-label=\"windows10 hyper v와 docker permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Windows10 Hyper-V와 Docker</h2>\n<p><strong>Windows10에서 Hyper-V를 통해 Docker에 Linux 가상화 환경을 제공합니다</strong>  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 690px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 114.6788990825688%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Docker OS Type\"\n        title=\"Docker OS Type\"\n        src=\"/static/d08c457c17c7b332445b582a8dc1bf61/36727/docker-info.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d08c457c17c7b332445b582a8dc1bf61/acf4b/docker-info.png 173w,\n/static/d08c457c17c7b332445b582a8dc1bf61/fc834/docker-info.png 345w,\n/static/d08c457c17c7b332445b582a8dc1bf61/36727/docker-info.png 690w,\n/static/d08c457c17c7b332445b582a8dc1bf61/13450/docker-info.png 981w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br>\n이를 통해 Docker는 OS-TYPE Linux로 동작하는 것을 확인 할 수 있습니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p>그러면 Hyper-V를 통해 Windows는 어떻게 Linux 환경을 제공할까요?<br>\nWindows10에서 Linux를 제공하는 방법은 2가지 입니다 👉 <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/virtualization/windowscontainers/deploy-containers/linux-containers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Windows 10의 Linux 컨테이너</a>    </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Linux VM를 통한 Linux 컨테이너 실행</li>\n<li>Hyper-V 격리 통한 Linux 컨테이너 실행</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 690px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.2185089974293%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"docker on windows\"\n        title=\"docker on windows\"\n        src=\"/static/671bc7286a05c4b15ef3b8db4a3d2e1a/36727/docker-on-windows.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/671bc7286a05c4b15ef3b8db4a3d2e1a/acf4b/docker-on-windows.png 173w,\n/static/671bc7286a05c4b15ef3b8db4a3d2e1a/fc834/docker-on-windows.png 345w,\n/static/671bc7286a05c4b15ef3b8db4a3d2e1a/36727/docker-on-windows.png 690w,\n/static/671bc7286a05c4b15ef3b8db4a3d2e1a/e7c6f/docker-on-windows.png 778w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>일반적으로 1번 방식을 통해 Docker는 Windows에서도 Linux Container를 동작합니다<br>\nClient는 Windows에 둔 상태에서 Daemon만을 이중으로 두고 운영환경에 맞게 동작됩니다   </p>\n<br/>\n<hr>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>참고로 Mac OS도 같은 이유로 Linux 환경을 제공할 가상환경이 필요합니다</strong><br>\nMac OS의 경우는 <code class=\"language-text\">Xhyve</code>라는 <code class=\"language-text\">Hypervisor</code>기반의 <code class=\"language-text\">HyperKit</code>를 통한 경량화 가상 기술을 사용합니다<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/machyve/xhyve\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Xhyve</a>은 Mac OS의 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhyve\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">bhyve</a> 버젼으로 <code class=\"language-text\">Type2형식</code>의 Hypervisor를 지원합니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 690px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.908904810644835%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Docker On Mac\"\n        title=\"Docker On Mac\"\n        src=\"/static/62e74ec053866bf3398c3d2479fb2400/36727/docker-for-mac-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62e74ec053866bf3398c3d2479fb2400/acf4b/docker-for-mac-install.png 173w,\n/static/62e74ec053866bf3398c3d2479fb2400/fc834/docker-for-mac-install.png 345w,\n/static/62e74ec053866bf3398c3d2479fb2400/36727/docker-for-mac-install.png 690w,\n/static/62e74ec053866bf3398c3d2479fb2400/6fc51/docker-for-mac-install.png 977w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span class='img_caption'>Source : <a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/docker-for-mac/docker-toolbox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Docker Desktop on Mac vs. Docker Toolbox</a></span></p>\n<br/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"관련-참고\"><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"관련 참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>관련 참고</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.docker.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Docker Bolg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@jwyeom63/%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%9C-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-vm-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B3%A0-%EB%8F%84%EC%BB%A4%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%BC%EA%B8%B0-3a04c000cb5c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">도커에 대한 이야기</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/virtualization/windowscontainers/manage-containers/hyperv-container\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hyper-V 격리</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.nebulaworks.com/blog/2017/04/23/getting-started-linuxkit-mac-os-x-xhyve/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LinuxKit on Mac OS X with xhyve</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Docker] Docker의 구조와 Windows10의 Docker","date":"March 09, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/docker/docker-structure-windows10/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/docker-setup/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Docker] Windows10 Docker 설치","category":"Docker"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/docker-hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Docker] Docker 시작하기 - Hello World와 Git Bash","category":"Docker"}}}}}